Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:38.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Fuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:40.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:46.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're only working for us until next year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:48.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:51.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:53.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have work back at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:57.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:03.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why don't we...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:08.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nevermind, I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:10.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the morning star.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:26.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seijirou-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:29.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,what do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:31.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:34.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a string coming from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:35.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A string?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:38.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder where it's coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:54.07,ep-title-bg,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2100,3170)\p1\blur1}m 0 0 l 950 0 950 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.18,0:02:54.06,ep-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2500,3200)\be1}String from the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:00.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:01.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stop crying,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:07.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,or we can't go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:10.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, the sky's full of stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:14.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder where that star went.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:17.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That comet with a tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:18.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,About the comet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:26.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which way was it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:36.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was waving and twinkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of such a comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:42.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it'd be a big discovery if they do exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:44.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm gonna find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were... Fuki, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice find.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:55.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, I never did find such a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:03.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We hired Fuki as a nanny for my troublesome sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'd say bizarre things occasionally,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:11.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the villagers often looked coldly on her for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:18.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Fuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:22.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:25.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's not here either, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:26.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:29.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She got tired of babysitting and ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That ungrateful girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:31.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:33.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuki would never...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:36.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'd never abandon her work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was trying to pull a "string" at the riverbed, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then she disappeared in front of my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:46.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seijirou-bocchan, can't you think\Nof some better excuses for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:57.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where've you gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:23.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:37.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:42.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:49.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}walking through the mountains with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:10.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got to drink this and get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't take care of you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:16.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to get better too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:19.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Better?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:22.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:25.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:31.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were exposed to a strong Mushi presence.\NYou've become something very ambiguous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:36.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt anyone else can see you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:38.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That white string coming out of your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:41.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be because you touched that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:43.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Left untreated,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:46.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,you'll become less and less human.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:52.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you helping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:54.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:57.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just doing what I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just gotta bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:15.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,you're starting to look better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:16.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:18.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:21.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're finding a village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:27.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll recover quicker if you're with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:31.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you can't remember anything, just\Nask a nearby village to let you stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But which way are we supposed to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:08:01.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something shining under the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:02.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:05.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet you can see it pretty well right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:09.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is a Koumyakusuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are those things shining?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:15.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's called Kouki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:20.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a swarm of preborn Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are Mushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:28.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,those small things hiding in the dark\Nor flying around in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:34.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't look at it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:38.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's toxic to your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:41.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you look at it for too long, you\Nwon't be able to see sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a river of light up above too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:49.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That one's shining even at night\Nwith the light from the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:52.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch this river instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:56.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:01.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like a reflection of the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're apples and oranges.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful not to get them confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I slept so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:27.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The girl didn't cry last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:29.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:34.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:40.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:47.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:50.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was living at the bottom of those mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:00.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:02.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Fuki, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:03.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one that disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:05.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Fuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:08.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just where did you run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:09.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:15.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We searched the mountain for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:17.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:25.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just pulled on a string dangling from the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then everything went black.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when I came to,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:32.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:37.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you run off and come home scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:40.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's a bit too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:43.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They already hired a new nanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:45.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:46.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seijirou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:54.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:55.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:59.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man over there helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:03.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, come to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:07.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on Fuki, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:11.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they already have a replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:14.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:17.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then come back as my bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided I'd tell you that when you got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:26.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:34.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:35.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:42.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:45.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is everything okay? It sounded like an argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:46.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:50.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect him to accept it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what was it that you wanted to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me what happened when Fuki disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:01.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure you'd believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:08.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuki said she saw a string dangling from the sky that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and she made a gesture like pulling\Nat something in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:13.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:17.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,she bolted up into the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:21.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and she disappeared high up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody believed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:36.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never thought much about the things\Nthat Fuki said she saw until I saw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:40.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. Tenpengusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a Mushi living high up in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:53.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're creatures of the yin, living on\Nthe border between yin and yang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:13:01.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuki called them "things hiding in the\Ndark and flying around in the sky".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:03.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't many that can see them,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:07.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but they exist everywhere in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:10.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can see those things Fuki sees too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:14.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I make a living dealing with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a little envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuki is quite a lucky woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But be careful for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:29.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She hasn't completely recovered\Nfrom the Mushi's influence yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:35.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tenpengusa usually take the form of balloons with tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:40.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They dwell in the skies above special\Nregions called Koumyakusuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:43.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They live on small light consuming Mushi in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:47.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,At night, they often look like squirming stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:52.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hence they also have the name Mayoiboshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:55.48,notes,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Mayoiboshi: a wandering, lost star
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:55.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,...that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:59.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was waving and twinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:04.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,At times when they can't get enough food,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:08.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,they extend their tentacles down close\Nto the surface like fishing lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:11.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They look like strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:18.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when an animal touches one,\Nit'll get pulled up into the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:21.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it will get tossed out because\Nthe Mushi can't consume it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:26.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most of the time they'll hit the ground and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:31.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuki got lucky; she landed on a tree and survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:34.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Fuki must have come close to being consumed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:38.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's had a strong exposure to the Mushi's presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:42.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you couldn't find her when you\Nwent to look for her in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:46.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuki had become invisible to the human eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:50.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's gotten better with this drug,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she's not fully recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:58.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's still in an unstable state, attached\Nto the sky with the string on her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it gets worse it'll happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:04.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,For Fuki to return to human,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:07.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,she needs more than just this drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:12.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She needs to have the will to remain human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:17.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's up to you to make her feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:21.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that's none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:24.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:26.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a shame you won't stay here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:34.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't stay for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:38.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be holding a wedding sometime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:41.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll come then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:48.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:53.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll see you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:57.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:03.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,the letter I received since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:17.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,was to inform me that Fuki vanished again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:21.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:30.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father wouldn't let us get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:35.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We spent a long time trying to persuade him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:39.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuki was having a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:45.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then Fuki slowly became lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time there was some wind,\Nshe'd flutter up into the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:55.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,As time passed, she became unable\Nto stay on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:56.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:58.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come down, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to get back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:05.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just when Dad's about to give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:08.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can't see you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:09.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't control my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:17.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay still, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:19.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And take the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:20.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:31.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:35.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find her anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:40.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:43.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to hold her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:45.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did what I could!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:48.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that everyone else would accept her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:50.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,with Fuki the way she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:54.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You, more than anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:58.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,are having a hard time accepting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:04.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because you rejected her that she\Ncan't sustain her human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:09.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't... sustain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:10.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't see her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:13.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:23.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to lose Fuki, you have to accept her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:25.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Accept her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't see or touch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:31.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the only one that can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:39.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The last thing keeping her here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,is your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:19:00.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:03.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:09.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seijirou-bocchan, why are you always looking at the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:14.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:19.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know when you have a bad day, you\Nlook at the stars and they're always there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,For some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:25.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I find it relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:32.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I get sad because the girl won't stop crying,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:35.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I count the stars to distract myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:42.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's a little disheartening when it starts getting bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:45.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They start disappearing one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:48.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and before I know it, they're all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:56.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder where they all are during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:58.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silly Fuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:01.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're still there during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:03.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:05.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:08.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just can't see them because the sun's so bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:10.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all there above the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:18.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They don't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:20.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you can't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:26.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're always there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:34.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:45.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a creepy sight to behold, they'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:49.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A marriage was held on short notice
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,without a bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:53.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet the groom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:56.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Drink up, Fuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:59.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,acted as if there was one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:02.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Or maybe... like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:08.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone whispered that the groom had gone mad too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:15.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Days passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:20.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he began living alone at the edge of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:27.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd still talk to his imaginary wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:33.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the villagers began to ostracize him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:44.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But eventually...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:46.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seijirou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:52.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't that... that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:54.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Fuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:56.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just when did she come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:02.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,People could see Fuki again,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:13.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and she lost her habit of disappearing.
